macandrews  forbes  macandrews  forbes incorporated macandrews  forbes maf t welcome to macandrews  forbes macandrews  forbes incorporated owns and operates a diverse array of businesses tapping into the broad expertise of its management team to support the delivery of best in class products and services to end users and consumers all over the world wholly owned by chairman and chief executive officer ronald o perelman macandrews  forbes’ primary objective is to build run and grow great businesses our core strategy is to focus our business lines on strong market positions high quality management with vertical expertise recognized growth potential and ability to increase productivity macandrews  forbes’ businesses span a wide range of industries from global leaders in cosmetics and digital entertainment to biotechnology and military equipment management  macandrews  forbes incorporated executive leadership management maf t ronald o perelman chairman and chief executive officer barry f schwartz executive vice chairman paul m meister president steven m cohen executive vice president chief administrative officer and general counsel debra g perelman executive vice president strategy and new business development paul g savas executive vice president and chief financial officer frances f townsend executive vice president worldwide government legal and business affairs mark m dowley chief strategy officer portfolio  macandrews  forbes incorporated portfolio portfolio maf t am general exchange privately held president  ceo andy hove hq south bend in wwwamgeneralcom deluxe exchange privately held ceo john wallace hq los angeles ca wwwbydeluxecom flavors holdings inc exchange privately held ceo albert manzone hq new york ny harland clarke holdings corp exchange privately held ceo victor nichols hq san antonio tx wwwharlandclarkeholdingscom harland clarke exchange privately held president  ceo dan singleton hq san antonio tx wwwharlandclarkecom mafco worldwide exchange privatel